Cell["\<\
A PacletInfo.wl or PacletInfo.m file containing metadata describing a paclet \
and its resources is essential for converting a directory or collection of \
files into a paclet.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"3d97f2d5-306b-484b-b3f9-68226dbe4327"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

